            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Another tip: I just noticed the `VCRUNTIMExxx.dll` issue mentioned in `INSTALL.md`. The `nightly.ps1` above actually will generate a singleton `winget` package manifest, so it can declare the`VCRedist` dependency and install it automatically if needed.\n\nFinally, I think this is probably all we can do on our side. The rest likely depends on how the `winget-pkgs` repo handles it. :D",
